!**/src/main/**/target/
!**/src/test/**/target/
# Local Claude Code pipeline output
# Reports are tracked in git so the latest assessment/remediation state is recoverable.
# Everything else under .claude/reports/ stays ignored.
.claude/reports/*
!.claude/reports/SECURITY_ASSESSMENT_REPORT.md
!.claude/reports/SECURE_REMEDIATION_REPORT.md
!.claude/reports/.gitkeep
